        descriptionSnippet:
            'High-security B2B file transfer and automation ecosystem.',
        bullets: [
            'Directed mobile engineering for a high-security B2B file transfer and automation ecosystem.',
            'Architected a "Hybrid-First" shared-logic strategy, achieving 90% business logic reuse between Web and Mobile platforms.',
            'Developed a global TypeScript component system to enforce design consistency at scale.',
            'Optimized large-scale list performance for 10k+ items via aggressive virtualization and memory management.',
