            'Migrated heritage Provider Portals to Angular, modernizing regional health infrastructure.',
            'Applied WCAG 2.0 standards to critical member portals to ensure universal access.',
        ],
    },

    {
        title: 'Loma Linda University Medical Center',
        category: 'Healthcare',
        href: 'https://murrieta.lluh.org/',
        image: lomaImage,
        bullets: [
            'Responsive and Pageless Design with Bootstrap and SASS, Wireframes with Bolsamiq, Coffeescript, Expression Engine.',
        ],
    },
]

